snippet.title: Speak on it with WhouwithCurtdog
snippet.description: Speak On It With WhouwithCurtdog is a Podcast located in Dallas, TX.  We will talk about what's going on in the world today.  We will give authors, musician, and actors the opportunity to share their work with us. Most importantly, allowing everyday people the opportunity and platform to speak openly on subjects that matters to them.  If you have any subject you would like for us to "Speak On," please email us at whouwithcurtdog@mail.com
